OL,3,GDumfries, Galloway, Lothian & Borders
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FCloudy this
OL,6,Fevening with outbreaks of rain
OL,7,Fspreading northwards over mainly
OL,8,Fwestern parts. Overnight it will be
OL,9,Fcloudy with outbreaks of rain
OL,10,Fspreading to all parts.
OL,11,
OL,12,CMonday:FA mostly cloudy day with
OL,13,Foutbreaks of rain. Becoming drier with
OL,14,Fbright spells for a time in the
OL,15,Fafternoon, best of these in the east.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
